      "file_path": "asdc-controller/src/main/java/org/onap/so/asdc/installer/heat/ToscaResourceInstaller.java",
      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 1330,
      "message": "I don't think this is necessary. We have recently implemented a feature where if tosca csar already exists, SDC is notified with ALREADY_DEPLOYED status & the current notification will not be processed any further. \nIn this case, it will always be a new service and I don't see the need for fetching a service from the database to verify if the service already exists.\nJeff can weigh-in.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4277,
        "name": "Ramesh Parthasarathy",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "ramesh.parthasarathy@att.com",
